'''達西·G·理查森'''（{{lang-en|Darcy G. Richardson}}；{{bd|1955年|12月6日}}），是美國一名[[作家|作家]]、[[史家|歷史學家]]及[[行动主义|政治活動家]]。

他曾在[[2012年美國總統選舉|2012年美國總統選舉]]五個州的[[民主黨_(美國)|民主黨]]初選中挑戰時任總統[[巴拉克·歐巴馬|巴拉克·歐巴馬]]的提名.<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.ballot-access.org/2011/10/21/darcy-richardson-files-in-new-hampshire-democratic-presidential-primary/ | title=Darcy Richardson Files in New Hampshire Democratic Presidential Primary | work=[[Ballot_Access_News|Ballot Access News]] | date=October 21, 2011 | accessdate=November 3, 2011 | author=[[Richard_Winger|Winger, Richard]] | archive-date=2021-02-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225053125/http://ballot-access.org/2011/10/21/darcy-richardson-files-in-new-hampshire-democratic-presidential-primary/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.boston.com/Boston/politicalintelligence/2011/10/primary-ballot-becomes-equalizer-between-top-tier-perennial-candidates/MkD7dWcT2Nq0gUe2Gv1GuM/index.html | title=N.H. primary ballot becomes equalizer between top-tier, perennial candidates | work=[[Boston_Globe|Boston Globe]] | date=October 28, 2011 | accessdate=November 4, 2011 | author=Schoenberg, Shira | archive-date=2011-10-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111030081008/http://www.boston.com/Boston/politicalintelligence/2011/10/primary-ballot-becomes-equalizer-between-top-tier-perennial-candidates/MkD7dWcT2Nq0gUe2Gv1GuM/index.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>，並曾在{{le|2018年佛羅里達州州長選舉|Florida gubernatorial election, 2018}}以{{le|佛羅里達改革黨|Reform Party of Florida}}名義參選州長<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.theledger.com/article/20101003/COLUMNISTS/10035055D | title=Write-ins and Independents Fill Out Ballot | work=The Ledger of LAKELAND | date=October 3, 2010 | accessdate=September 26, 2012 | archive-date=2016-04-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160413041144/http://www.theledger.com/article/20101003/COLUMNISTS/10035055D | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2020年，他以[[美国改革党|改革党]]與[[和平與自由黨|和平與自由黨]]身份競逐[[2020年美國總統選舉|2020年美國總統選舉]]的副總統職務，其競選搭檔為[[洛基·德拉富恩特|洛基·德拉富恩特]].<ref name=Alliance>{{cite web|url=https://independentpoliticalreport.com/2020/04/darcy-richardson-discusses-the-alliance-party/|title=Darcy Richardson Discusses the Alliance Party|website=Independent Political Report|last1=Saturn|first1=William|date=April 11, 2020|accessdate=April 17, 2020|archive-date=2020-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201207045858/https://independentpoliticalreport.com/2020/04/darcy-richardson-discusses-the-alliance-party/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

